result.name: Plover Cove Garden Arcade

reviews.text:
Local small mall very poorly managed with one dim sum place.. another cross the road. 
Few local small food stores that are not recommended.
The shopping centre is untidily and the shops uninteresting e.g poorly oldie from the 90’s .
People’s use as a past through to Tai Po or Tai Po centres.
Mail is good for company looking for a mall for redevelopment, the draw back could be the ownership of market part and part of the mall.
Great view with warm firewood. Nice place to stay with family.

Poorly managed shopping centre and residential development. The shopping centre is messy, smelly and the shops uninteresting. There’s a small Tesco store (called U Select), which can be useful. There’s a decent dimsum restaurant. On the G/F level the exits of the parking lot can be dangerous, as drivers wrongly believe they have right of way leaving an building exit.
Nothing of interest here, I only walk through here to get to tai po megamall from tai po mtr
With some small travel agencies, real estate agencies....well small shops

result.name: 寶湖花園商場

reviews.text: 一般般啦😄
有洒樓，超市，診所，商鋪等，旅行社多間，中旅，美味，德興等。
這裡有酒樓易找到座位，價錢普通可接受，這商埸商務沒有名牌商，街市十有九空。
因為地方闊樂有酒樓和各種不同食品，衣服，地產及多間旅遊地點，下層是街市全部應有盡有。🙌👍
"楼上"对面檔鷄蛋仔好食，脆及Q，尤其中意咖啡味，盛载杯仔乾淨兼新潮。

result.name: 彩福喜宴

reviews.text: Great food
價$太貴，下午茶，茶$11/位，菜式味道太普通
飲茶時間食物質素很好， 枱與枱距離合理， 感覺良好
星期日晚上在此酒樓食晚飯，點了一個套餐，食物質素比預期好，算中上水平。可惜上菜次序比較亂，完全冇次序，煮熟便上菜。服務只屬一般，侍應不足，全程没有換過碟。地方算闊落，但似乎客人太多以致過於嘈雜。
食品有水準 多款燉湯必食
